column2: what is the closest el rancho grande ?
column3: ( [ * , distance ( geo , $location . current_location ) ] of sort ( distance ( geo , $location . current_location ) asc of @org.schema.Restaurant . Restaurant ( ) filter name =~ " el rancho grande " ) ) [ 1 ] ;

column2: where is the nearest indian restaurant ?
column3: [ geo ] of ( [ * , distance ( geo , $location . current_location ) ] of sort ( distance ( geo , $location . current_location ) asc of @org.schema.Restaurant . Restaurant ( ) filter servesCuisine =~ " indian " ) ) [ 1 ] ;

column2: show me the review for hollins street pub by johneka roy
column3: ( @org.schema.Restaurant . Restaurant ( ) filter id == null ^^org.schema.Restaurant:Restaurant ( " hollins street pub " ) => @org.schema.Restaurant . Review ( ) ) filter author == null ^^org.schema.Restaurant:Person ( " johneka roy " ) && in_array ( id , review ) ;

column2: how well is park inn rated ?
column3: [ aggregateRating.ratingValue ] of @org.schema.Restaurant . Restaurant ( ) filter id == null ^^org.schema.Restaurant:Restaurant ( " park inn " ) ;

column2: what is the rating of that north pole ice cream company ' ?
column3: [ aggregateRating.ratingValue ] of @org.schema.Restaurant . Restaurant ( ) filter id == null ^^org.schema.Restaurant:Restaurant ( " north pole ice cream company " ) ;
